<item>
            <title>[LU-11226] sanity-flr test 200 fails with &apos;checksum error for mirror 3&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11226</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanity-flr test_200 started failing on August 6, 2018. The last lines seen in the test_log is&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;/mnt/lustre/f200.sanity-flr: found 6 stale components
/mnt/lustre/f200.sanity-flr: resyncing mirror: 1, components: 65537 65538 65539 65540 
components synced: 65537 65538 65539 65540 
/mnt/lustre/f200.sanity-flr: resyncing mirror: 3, components: 196609 196610 
components synced: 196609 196610 
3
 sanity-flr test_200: @@@@@@ FAIL: checksum error for mirror 3
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There&#8217;s nothing interesting in the node console logs for this test. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Looking at all the patches that landed around August 6, &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/32808&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/32808&lt;/a&gt; looks like a possible candidate for a change in the mirror resync behavior. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here are links to a few recent failures:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/71ef290a-9a2d-11e8-8ee3-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/71ef290a-9a2d-11e8-8ee3-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/5ee037ee-99d0-11e8-87f3-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/5ee037ee-99d0-11e8-87f3-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/4cb6a618-99bf-11e8-a9f7-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/4cb6a618-99bf-11e8-a9f7-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
